relation: Darrow1 - #60 Giygas begins to take stronger measures in preventing the three heroes, but is unaware of how inept his minions can be. Unfortunately for the Boogie Tent...he is a monster...that inhabits a tent...and therefore not much of a threat.
Darrow3 - #11 The return to the real world proves to be a happy occasion, though the troubles Ness and Jeff must face are far from over.

Darrow3 - #75 Nothing better to wrap up the day than a nice, juicy steak! The dinner table is a time for relaxing and talking about your day. It's also apparently the time to reveal your brother's most embarrassing past secrets.
Darrow6 - #30 Paula and Jeff spring into action, enraged at the golem's attempt to land the final blow on Poo.
Darrow - #71 With the pencil statue erased, it's time to move on! Unfortunately for Ness, that means he is now subjected to Peaceful Rest Valley's trials.
